Greetings <%= @host.complete_name  %>

You have new booking request for your property <%= link_to @offer.translations.first.title, offer_url(@offer)  %>.

The booking details are as follows:


<table>
  <tr>
    <td>Checkin Date</td>
    <td><%= @trip.checkin %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Checkout Date</td>
    <td><%= @trip.checkout  %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Guest Name</td>
    <td><%= @guest.complete_name %></td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>No of Guest</td>
    <td><%= @trip.guest_count %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

To accept the request click on the link Below:
<%= link_to 'YES', trip_url(@trip, e: @guest.email,t: @guest.email_token,b: @trip.id,a: 'y')  %>
To Decline click No.
<%= link_to 'NO', trip_url(@trip, e: @guest.email,t: @guest.email_token,b: @trip.id,a: 'n')  %>


Thanks for using Roomnhouse Services.
